{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-contents-markdown-remark-frontmatter-slug-tsx","path":"/contents/17th-algorithm-study-memoir/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"좋은-학습-방향을-얻다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A2%8B%EC%9D%80-%ED%95%99%EC%8A%B5-%EB%B0%A9%ED%96%A5%EC%9D%84-%EC%96%BB%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"좋은 학습 방향을 얻다 permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>좋은 학습 방향을 얻다</h1>\n<p><span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/f136830562d20f7c8018ae6bea5d977b/f55e8/book.jpg' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 130.67484662576686%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='book' title='book' src='/static/f136830562d20f7c8018ae6bea5d977b/6aca1/book.jpg' srcset='/static/f136830562d20f7c8018ae6bea5d977b/d2f63/book.jpg 163w,\n/static/f136830562d20f7c8018ae6bea5d977b/c989d/book.jpg 325w,\n/static/f136830562d20f7c8018ae6bea5d977b/6aca1/book.jpg 650w,\n/static/f136830562d20f7c8018ae6bea5d977b/f55e8/book.jpg 918w' sizes='(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\r\n또 공부노선을 틀었다.</p>\n<p>이번엔 충분히 그럴만한 가치가 있었다.</p>\n<p>업무 관련해서 <strong><a href=\"http://www.yes24.com/Product/Goods/91084402?pid=123487&#x26;cosemkid=go15947993245566115&#x26;gclid=Cj0KCQiApb2bBhDYARIsAChHC9sDZYpm258UTd97tuOMLPUIUAt3v4urxPLO2YHQ5SPYcNMMQ878Q18aAgffEALw_wcB\">파이썬 알고리즘 인터뷰</a></strong> 책을 받아서 읽어봤는데, 단순히 알고리즘에 대한 내용이 아닌\r\n파이썬이라는 언어를 두고 c, java, go 등 다양한 컴퓨터 프로그래밍 언어를 비교하면서 어떤 점이 특징이고</p>\n<p>왜 우리가 파이썬을 이용해서 코테를 대비해야하는 지 알려준다.</p>\n<p>책을 보며 몇몇 문제를 해결했고, 파이썬이 무작정 느리다는 편견을 깨부숴줬다.</p>\n<p>더불어 필자는 앞으로 파이썬에 익숙해져야 한다고 생각한다.</p>\n<p>언어는 점점 빨라지고, 사용 사례는 점점 넓어지고 있기 때문이다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"노마드-코더의-얼마나-빨라진거야-파이썬-업그레이드-3분-정리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%85%B8%EB%A7%88%EB%93%9C-%EC%BD%94%EB%8D%94%EC%9D%98-%EC%96%BC%EB%A7%88%EB%82%98-%EB%B9%A8%EB%9D%BC%EC%A7%84%EA%B1%B0%EC%95%BC-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%B4%EC%8D%AC-%EC%97%85%EA%B7%B8%EB%A0%88%EC%9D%B4%EB%93%9C-3%EB%B6%84-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"노마드 코더의 얼마나 빨라진거야 파이썬 업그레이드 3분 정리 permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hgmz0NJugEc&#x26;t=103s\">노마드 코더의 \"얼마나 빨라진거야? 파이썬 업그레이드 3분 정리!\"</a></h4>\n<h1 id=\"valid-palindrome-leetcode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#valid-palindrome-leetcode\" aria-label=\"valid palindrome leetcode permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Valid Palindrome [LeetCode]</h1>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"py\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"material\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">\r\nclass Solution:\r\n    def is_palindrome_convert_to_list(self, s: str) -&gt; bool:\r\n        strs = []\r\n        for c in s:\r\n            if c.isalnum():\r\n                strs.append(c.lower())\r\n        while len(strs) &gt; 1:\r\n            if strs.pop(0) != strs.pop():\r\n                return False\r\n        return True\r\n\r\n    def is_palindrome_deque(self, s: str) -&gt; bool:\r\n        deque = collections.deque()\r\n        for c in s:\r\n            if c.isalnum():\r\n                deque.append(c.lower())\r\n        while len(deque) &gt; 1:\r\n            if deque.pop() != deque.popleft():\r\n                return False\r\n        return True\r\n\r\n    def is_palindrome_slicing(self, s: str) -&gt; bool:\r\n        s = s.lower()\r\n        s = re.sub(r&#39;[^a-z0-9]&#39;, &#39;&#39;, s)\r\n        return s == s[::-1]</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>8월 달 즘에 자바로 해결했었던 문제다.</p>\n<p>그리 어려운 문제는 아니었으며 예제 코드가 길어보이는 이유는\r\n3가지 해결 방안으로 문제를 해결했기 때문이다.</p>\n<p>핵심 코드는 다음과 같다.</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"py\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"material\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">    def is_palindrome_slicing(self, s: str) -&gt; bool:\r\n        s = s.lower()\r\n        s = re.sub(r&#39;[^a-z0-9]&#39;, &#39;&#39;, s)\r\n        return s == s[::-1]</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>파이썬의 문자열 슬라이싱을 이용하면 코드의 성능이 우월해진다.</p>\n<p>슬라이싱 문법을 이용하면 문자열의 포인터 값이 바로 전달되기 때문이라고 한다.</p>\n<p>다음은 위에서 순서대로 해결까지 걸린 시간(ms) 정보다.</p>\n<p>list , deque , slicing 순\r\n<span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/5a36ba3e8c99e9fe04c997ff7094322d/bb051/palindrome_list.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 15.337423312883436%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAAdklEQVQI12WNWQoCMRBEc/+LeAkv4bcI+q8jiGbt6idJRnGwmuJBL9XhFRPLcqfWwpRv6Y5/zORsT5oMy43D9cjuvCekClWsQ8cE8pGzhvzo+8P/LBe9Ai5iSuQmqkFuPqix2I/F6SZiMdIzovFtG9rVsvG4FN4HwuwryHN5JQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='list' title='list' src='/static/5a36ba3e8c99e9fe04c997ff7094322d/a6d36/palindrome_list.png' srcset='/static/5a36ba3e8c99e9fe04c997ff7094322d/222b7/palindrome_list.png 163w,\n/static/5a36ba3e8c99e9fe04c997ff7094322d/ff46a/palindrome_list.png 325w,\n/static/5a36ba3e8c99e9fe04c997ff7094322d/a6d36/palindrome_list.png 650w,\n/static/5a36ba3e8c99e9fe04c997ff7094322d/e548f/palindrome_list.png 975w,\n/static/5a36ba3e8c99e9fe04c997ff7094322d/bb051/palindrome_list.png 1212w' sizes='(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\r\n<span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/8569bfb6957e82d77c36153ba3b95a60/f8836/palindrome_deque.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 17.177914110429448%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAAeklEQVQI122NSw7CMBBDe/9LcQN2rFghNrDj1yRNxn6oDYhWYiTLsjV6Hl5p4vEciWj08x/3Kn/bniWhKo73M7vrnqEGNEEYapgpWCSDbWwoweIOf7qfNrsBgy1yztQmQjPczCNS/5xacLgEuVTSmLA6ZAMFyti4nQpvS1PscFZ1mjEAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='deque' title='deque' src='/static/8569bfb6957e82d77c36153ba3b95a60/a6d36/palindrome_deque.png' srcset='/static/8569bfb6957e82d77c36153ba3b95a60/222b7/palindrome_deque.png 163w,\n/static/8569bfb6957e82d77c36153ba3b95a60/ff46a/palindrome_deque.png 325w,\n/static/8569bfb6957e82d77c36153ba3b95a60/a6d36/palindrome_deque.png 650w,\n/static/8569bfb6957e82d77c36153ba3b95a60/e548f/palindrome_deque.png 975w,\n/static/8569bfb6957e82d77c36153ba3b95a60/f8836/palindrome_deque.png 1214w' sizes='(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\r\n<span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/df1596d1c15a5ca41f0ad1325d1ae764/20f89/palindrome_slicing.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 14.723926380368097%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAAeUlEQVQI11WNSw7CMBBDc/+7cAd2HABO0BViE1S1aZjfQylpAI8sjUceO83LSs4ZVeWD+CFExJd9jnuDmmFVuTxunKYzqQhoNAOYB+rgXR9PA13+lexGRlkKN9ZSEQvEoGrsu/ewTZzrPRAxylIIj1E2ApvvKczTizf9HewF4b4QkAAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='slicing' title='slicing' src='/static/df1596d1c15a5ca41f0ad1325d1ae764/a6d36/palindrome_slicing.png' srcset='/static/df1596d1c15a5ca41f0ad1325d1ae764/222b7/palindrome_slicing.png 163w,\n/static/df1596d1c15a5ca41f0ad1325d1ae764/ff46a/palindrome_slicing.png 325w,\n/static/df1596d1c15a5ca41f0ad1325d1ae764/a6d36/palindrome_slicing.png 650w,\n/static/df1596d1c15a5ca41f0ad1325d1ae764/e548f/palindrome_slicing.png 975w,\n/static/df1596d1c15a5ca41f0ad1325d1ae764/20f89/palindrome_slicing.png 1213w' sizes='(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"reorder-data-in-log-files-leetcode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reorder-data-in-log-files-leetcode\" aria-label=\"reorder data in log files leetcode permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reorder Data in Log Files [LeetCode]</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/reorder-data-in-log-files/description/\">Reorder Data in Log Files</a></p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"py\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"material\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">class Solution:\r\n    def reorderLogFiles(self, logs: List[str]) -&gt; List[str]:\r\n        letters, digits = [], []\r\n        for log in logs:\r\n            if log.split()[1].isdigit():\r\n                digits.append(log)\r\n            else:\r\n                letters.append(log)\r\n        letters.sort(key=lambda x: (x.split()[1:], x.split()[0]))\r\n        return letters + digits</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>파이썬에서 문자열 데이터를 조건으로 처리할 때 얼마나 직관적으로 처리하느냐에 관한 문제다.</p>\n<p>파이썬 람다 키워드 사용방법이 신기했고, 다른 언어에도 있는 개념이라 어렵지 않게 습득했다.</p>\n<p>리스트 끼리 + 연산할 수 있다는 것이 신선했다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"group-anagrams-leetcode\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#group-anagrams-leetcode\" aria-label=\"group anagrams leetcode permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Group Anagrams [LeetCode]</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/group-anagrams/\">Group Anagrams</a></p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"py\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"material\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">class Solution:\r\n    def groupAnagrams(self, strs: List[str]): # -&gt; List[List[str]]:\r\n        anagrams = collections.defaultdict(list)\r\n\r\n        for word in strs:\r\n            anagrams[&#39;&#39;.join(sorted(word))].append(word)\r\n        return list(anagrams.values())</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>같은 철자들이 들어간 단어끼리 리스트로 그룹화하는 문제다.\r\n해시 테이블을 활용하면 간단하게 해결할 수 있는데\r\n짧게 쓸 수 있어서 조금 벙쪘다.</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"py\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"material\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">    anagrams = collections.defaultdict(list)</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>인자로 list 객체를 넣은 이유는 없는 값을 조회할 때 KeyError 발생을 방지하기 위함이다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"회고-마무리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%9A%8C%EA%B3%A0-%EB%A7%88%EB%AC%B4%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"회고 마무리 permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>회고 마무리</h1>\n<p><span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 366px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/0977bfef515ae06a5b91ecec61da02d6/8b153/my_condition.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 122.69938650306749%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='내 풀이 현황 이미지' title='내 풀이 현황 이미지' src='/static/0977bfef515ae06a5b91ecec61da02d6/8b153/my_condition.png' srcset='/static/0977bfef515ae06a5b91ecec61da02d6/222b7/my_condition.png 163w,\n/static/0977bfef515ae06a5b91ecec61da02d6/ff46a/my_condition.png 325w,\n/static/0977bfef515ae06a5b91ecec61da02d6/8b153/my_condition.png 366w' sizes='(max-width: 366px) 100vw, 366px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>c 로 해결한 문제는 사실 python 이다. 서비스에 버그가 있는 것이다 ㅠㅠ..</p>\n<p>요새 Spring Boot 2.7.5 로 백엔드 개발을 수행 중인데 너무 어렵다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"참고\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"참고 permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://alg-study-helper-chi.vercel.app/\">알고리즘 스터디 웹 서비스</a></p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%A2%8B%EC%9D%80-%ED%95%99%EC%8A%B5-%EB%B0%A9%ED%96%A5%EC%9D%84-%EC%96%BB%EB%8B%A4\">좋은 학습 방향을 얻다</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EB%85%B8%EB%A7%88%EB%93%9C-%EC%BD%94%EB%8D%94%EC%9D%98-%EC%96%BC%EB%A7%88%EB%82%98-%EB%B9%A8%EB%9D%BC%EC%A7%84%EA%B1%B0%EC%95%BC-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%B4%EC%8D%AC-%EC%97%85%EA%B7%B8%EB%A0%88%EC%9D%B4%EB%93%9C-3%EB%B6%84-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC\">노마드 코더의 \"얼마나 빨라진거야? 파이썬 업그레이드 3분 정리!\"</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#valid-palindrome-leetcode\">Valid Palindrome [LeetCode]</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#reorder-data-in-log-files-leetcode\">Reorder Data in Log Files [LeetCode]</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#group-anagrams-leetcode\">Group Anagrams [LeetCode]</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%ED%9A%8C%EA%B3%A0-%EB%A7%88%EB%AC%B4%EB%A6%AC\">회고 마무리</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\">참고</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"11월 2주차 알고리즘 스터디 회고록","date":"2022년 11월 13일","slug":"17th-algorithm-study-memoir","tag":["Algorithm"]}}},"pageContext":{"id":"0cf584ca-274a-5aff-bd6d-aeef00daad3e","frontmatter__slug":"17th-algorithm-study-memoir","__params":{"frontmatter__slug":"17th-algorithm-study-memoir"}}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}